      "content": "Hello and thank you for your quick response! Great that the dates work out, then we would like to book a fixed appointment for Friday, November 14 (we will arrive late on Thursday evening, so this will be our only option, I guess). As I said, it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s two small tattoos, both with the same motif. \n\nWe\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll think about the location again. Thank you for your comments. I know that the outside of the hand isn\u00e2\u0080\u0099t that easy (the picture is my tattoo), but maybe we\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll come up with something better.\n\nIf you need any further information from me, please let me know!",
