      "sender_name": "2310tattoo studio by Christina",
      "timestamp_ms": 1760379220606,
      "content": "The dates are fine \u00e2\u0080\u0094 the issue is the placement.\n\nWe do take on tattoos on fingers and the outer palm; however, we\u00e2\u0080\u0099d like to inform you that due to the unique nature of the skin in this area, the longevity of the result cannot be guaranteed. In some cases, the tattoo may fade or lose parts even within a few days, as it is affected by factors such as friction and the healing process. Getting a tattoo on the fingers is entirely at your own responsibility, and if a touch-up session is needed, the cost is \u00e2\u0082\u00ac15. We just want you to be fully informed before proceeding, so you have realistic expectations. We\u00e2\u0080\u0099re here for any questions you may have!",
